text: FC Pinzgau Saalfelden is an Austrian football club from Saalfelden in the federal state of Salzburg. The club currently plays in the Austrian Regionalliga Salzburg which is the third tier of Austrian football.https://vereine.fussballoesterreich.at/FcPinzgauSaalfelden/News/ ==History== The club was founded on 23 May 2007. The new club was formed out of 1.
